{"tid":2296802,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"佢究竟係唔係鐘意我","createTime":"2020-11-22T19:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T00:41:44.000Z","uid":385186,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bf1aec0c319d1b6ba770559e6878c459545522bc","tid":2296802,"uid":385186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T19:12:47.000Z","msg":"生日會比驚喜我<br />\n<br />\n我無帶錢出街佢即刻特登係屋企出來救我<br />\n但佢明明好多asm趕<br />\n<br />\n好多時都會遷就我<br />\n我想做咩都會陪我<br />\n<br />\n又會間中摸下我個頭<br />\n<br />\n會間中sd下心心emoij<br />\n<br />\n會送野比我<br />\n<br />\n但佢又遲遲唔表白<br />\n<br />\n定我會錯意佢唔係鐘意我<br />\n我身邊d frd係咁叫我睇定d先<br />\n未必係鐘意<br />\n<br />\n如果佢搵啱時機（聖誕節）表白我應該會應承<br />\n<br />\n但萬一佢聖誕節都唔表白，我同佢表白會唔會好尷"},{"pid":"0208bab0784c843fa7397104c9ad6ef0b953a924","tid":2296802,"uid":154054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T19:15:37.000Z","msg":"一個人溝緊幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da4bbec03767821d073257d94e196e75c241bdc","tid":2296802,"uid":385186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0208bab0784c843fa7397104c9ad6ef0b953a924","tid":2296802,"uid":154054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T19:15:37.000Z","msg":"一個人溝緊幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T19:23:02.000Z","msg":"得呢個<br />\n上次開po嗰個我無溝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2af2dd8e7b8793ba83c5b12301aa0ca18ef407a","tid":2296802,"uid":34047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T19:24:00.000Z","msg":"不如你比一啲佢一定get到既暗示佢先<br />\n<br />\n因為佢做既野可以係鍾意你 亦可以唔係<br />\n有啲男仔真心會重視同女仔既友誼"},{"pid":"aef8433c5efcf0acfb8e546df4fcc6dda81419ed","tid":2296802,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T19:24:57.000Z","msg":"Player"},{"pid":"cbbbe91fade79e7e5c3589e2878ab31a7bc8ab79","tid":2296802,"uid":154054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2da4bbec03767821d073257